  "description": {
   "en": "The Solminati Academy is a prestigious school that harbors the dreams and hopes of ambitious students. Our story resolves a young man named Nozomu Bountis who entered the school for his lover's dream. As time went on, his powers deadlocked and could no longer advance, and his grades fell. Eventually, his lover was stolen by his at-the-time best friend. Heartbroken and lost on what to do next, he focused even harder on his training. Eventually, he meets an Old woman, who triggers the catalyst to his growth. The future is uncertain but gradually, his world changes.  \n  \n  \n  \n  \n[Web Novel](https://ncode.syosetu.com/n7408y/)",
   "id": "Akademi solminati adalah sekolah bergengsi yang menampung impian dan harapan siswa yang ambisius. Kisah kami menyelesaikan seorang pemuda bernama Nozomu Bountis yang masuk sekolah untuk impian kekasihnya. Seiring berjalannya waktu, kekuatannya menemui jalan buntu dan tidak bisa lagi maju, dan nilainya turun. Akhirnya, kekasihnya dicuri oleh sahabatnya saat itu. Patah hati dan kehilangan apa yang harus dilakukan selanjutnya, dia lebih fokus pada pelatihannya. Akhirnya, dia bertemu dengan seorang wanita tua, yang memicu katalis untuk pertumbuhannya. Masa depan tidak pasti tetapi secara bertahap, dunianya berubah."
  },
